Returns the first and all the rest of the elements of the slice, or `None` if it is empty.

# Examples

```
let x = &[0, 1, 2];

if let Some((first, elements)) = x.split_first() {
    assert_eq!(first, &0);
    assert_eq!(elements, &[1, 2]);
}
```
